       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6BO05.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-BO-REVIEW.
           05  WS-PARTNER-PCT        PIC 9(3) VALUE ZERO.
               88  LEGACY-BO-RANGE  VALUE 16 THRU 100.
           05  WS-REVIEW-CODE        PIC X(4) VALUE 'PASS'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-PARTNER-PCT
           PERFORM 2400-SET-REVIEW-CODE
           DISPLAY WS-REVIEW-CODE
           STOP RUN.
       2400-SET-REVIEW-CODE.
           IF LEGACY-BO-RANGE
              MOVE 'BO' TO WS-REVIEW-CODE
           ELSE
              MOVE 'PASS' TO WS-REVIEW-CODE
           END-IF.
